[normal]development by the BBFC and NICAM of a User Generated Content (UGC) ratings tool. 
[normal] This self-regulatory questionnaire is tailored to reflect national differences and is designed to be completed by those uploading the content or the audience, allowing the use of online filters to prevent children accessing inappropriate content and the f
[normal]acility to report abuse.  
